Given a parameter, you can get the number of keyframes for any one of its channels. For a slider, toggle button (checkbox), or angle parameter, there will be only 1 channel (indexed starting at
), whereas a point parameter will have 2 channels (x and y), and a color channel will have 4 (R, G, B, and A).
